,100,1,0,0,'Text 4'),(27159,1,0,'We have been through worse and survived, Leoric. Do not forget Hyjal...',12,0,100,1,0,0,'Text 2'),(27159,2,0,'Say no more, Leoric. We all feel the chill in our bones. Yet, each day, heroes arrive from across the world -- and beyond.',12,0,100,1,0,0,'Text 3'),(27159,0,0,'It does get worse, old friend. According to my calculations, without suitable materials to repair our parapets, the walls protecting this keep will crumble in twelve hours.',12,0,100,1,0,0,'Text 1'),(21295,5,0,'COILSSSKARRR!',12,0,100,15,0,0,'Coilskar Commander'),(27191,0,0,'I\'m gonna jump this time Brote, I swear it!',12,0,100,1,0,0,'Text 1'),(27198,2,0,'I hope one of us dies. I hope that one is you, Skrotee.',12,0,100,1,0,0,'Text 3'),(27198,3,0,'Of all the hair--brained, idiotic, BRAINLESS ideas... \"Yeah Brote, it\'ll be great... The Forsaken will rain gold coins down on our heads!\"',12,0,100,1,0,0,'Text 4'),(27198,4,0,'This is all your fault, you know...',12,0,100,1,0,0,'Text 5'),(27198,1,0,'And you know what pisses me off more than anything, Skrotee? No, not that we\'ve been made into a living cuckoo clock for the amusement of the Forsaken. And not that we have to endure being spat upon and mocked every waking minute of our time here... What pisses me off the most is being made to wear these damned short--shorts...',12,0,100,1,0,0,'Text 2'),(27209,0,0,'Come to play?',12,0,100,0,0,0,'combat Say'),(27235,0,0,'Renounce the Scarlet Onslaught! Don\'t listen to the lies of the high general and the grand admiral any longer!',14,0,100,5,0,0,'Lead Cannoneer Zierhut'),(27236,0,0,'Abbendis is nothing but a harlot and Grand Admiral Westwind is selling her cheap like he sold us out!',14,0,100,5,0,0,'Stable Master Mercer'),(27234,0,0,'You are being misled! The Onslaught is all lies! The Scourge and the Forsaken are not our enemies! Wake up!',14,0,100,5,0,0,'Blacksmith Goodman'),(27237,0,0,'High general Abbendis personally told me that it was a mistake to come north and that 