enant. They were murdered.',12,0,100,1,3,0,'Stormwind investigator 1st sentence'),(42391,4,0,'Between you, me, and the tree, murlocs killed the Furlbrows. Yep, saw \'em with my own two eyes. Think they\'d been casin\' the joint for days, maybe months. They left in a hurry once they got wind of \"Johnny Law\" and the idiot brigade over there...',12,0,100,1,6000,0,'Murder was the case 4th clue'),(42391,3,0,'Who killed the Furlbrows? I\'ll tell you who killed the Furlbrows: KING VARIAN WRYNN. THAT\'S WHO! And he\'s killin\' the rest of us too. Once bum at a time. The only thing I can tell you is that I saw some gnolls leavin\' the place a few hours before the law arrived.',12,0,100,1,5000,0,'Murder was the case 3rd clue'),(42391,2,0,'I didn\'t see who killed \'em, $Gbub:sis , but I got a whiff. Smelled rich, kinda like you. Damn shame too. Furlbrows were a fixture around here. Nice people, always willin\' to share a meal or a patch of dirt.',12,0,100,1,5000,0,'Murder was the case 2nd clue'),(42391,1,0,'Listen, pal. I don\'t want any trouble, ok? I didn\'t see who murdered \'em, but I sure heard it! Lots of yelling. Human voices... you dig? Now get out of here before I change my mind about beating you up and takin\' your shoes.',12,0,100,1,5000,0,'Murder was the case 1st clue'),(42391,0,0,'I ain\'t tellin\' you a damn thing!',12,0,100,1,3000,0,'Murder was the case 1st aggro sentence'),(42391,0,1,'You rich punks are all the same!',12,0,100,1,3000,0,'Murder was the case 2nd aggro sentence'),(42391,0,2,'Now you\'v\'e gone and done it! TIME FOR THE FIST!',12,0,100,1,3000,0,'Murder was the case 3rd aggro sentence'),(42750,0,0,'You have our full cooperation, lieutenant. The Furlbrows were good people. Their deaths will not go unpunished.',12,0,100,1,3,0,'Gryan Stoutmantle 1st sentence'),(42308,2,0,'...Before the horse.',12,0,100,1,3,0,'Horatio Laine 3rd sentence'),(42750,2,0,'Do you know anything about this, beast? Speak!',12,0,100,1,3,0,'Gryan Stoutmantle In Defense of Westfall end event 1st sentence'),(42387,6,0,'DIE!',12,0,100,1,3000,0,'Thug 7th sentence'),(42387,5,0,'Only one thing to do with a lousy, good-for-nothin eavesdropper.',12,0,100,1,3000,0,'Thug 6th sentence'),(42387,3,0,'See her face? Is it really...',12,0,100,1,3000,0,'Thug 4th sentence'),(42387,4,0,'Whoa, what do we have here? Looks like we have ourselves an eavesdropper, boys.',12,0,100,1,3000,0,'Thug 5th sentence'),(42387,2,0,'She wanted me to tell you lugs that she appreciates the job that we did for her on the Furlbrows. gave me a pile o\' gold to split with you all.',12,0,100,1,3000,0,'Thug 3rd sentence'),(42387,1,0,'Yep. She\'s for real.',12,0,100,1,3000,0,'Thug 2nd sentence'),(42387,0,0,'Did you... Did you meet her?',12,0,100,1,3000,0,'Thug 1st sentence'),(42750,3,0,'Gibberish from a mad wolf. Bah!',12,0,100,1,3,0,'Gryan Stoutmantle In Defense of Westfall end event 2nd sentence'),(7024,0,3,'Got him!',15,0,100,1,3,0,'Agent Kearnen random sentence'),(42635,1,0,'The dawning comes, Stoutmantle, and with it comes your end.',12,0,100,1,3,0,'Ripsnarl  In Defense of Westfall end event 1st sentence'),(42308,7,0,'In his mouth.',12,0,100,1,3000,0,'Horatio Laine Lou\'s murder 5th sentence'),(42308,12,0,'Worse than your bite?',12,0,100,1,3,0,'Horatio Laine 5th sentence'),(42308,6,0,'It would appear that poor Lou readlly did put his foot...',12,0,100,1,3000,0,'Horatio Laine Lou\'s murder 4th sentence'),(42308,11,0,'But is your bark....',12,0,100,1,3,0,'Horatio Laine 4th sentence'),(42308,4,0,'This was an execution. Whoever did this was sending a message.',12,0,100,1,3000,0,'Horatio Laine Lou\'s murder 2nd sentence'),(42308,5,0,'A message for anyone that would dare snitch on these criminals.',12,0,100,1,3000,0,'Horatio Laine Lou\'s murder 3rd sentence'),(42308,3,0,'Doesn\'t look good, rookie.',12,0,100,1,3000,0,'Horatio Laine Lou\'s murder 1st sentence'),(42635,0,0,'When I break out of these stocks I\'m going to rip out your heart and devour it whole!',12,0,100,1,3,0,'Ripsnarl 